display_long_description:
Graffiti Legend is a unique spray simulator engine.
Create unique and digital high quality graffiti and art pieces.

Imagine having a 4-story building to yourself to create art! With GraffCity, you can make digital masterpieces in massive 4096x2048 and 8192x8192 (8K) resolutions  or a 6-story 8192x12288. Just remember, these stunning creations can be quite large files, so make sure you have plenty of storage space.

Become a true digital GRAFFITI LEGEND artist
